description: Lists information about dataset contents that have been created.

parameters.name: datasetName
parameters.description: The name of the dataset whose contents information you want to list.

nested_items.name: datasetContentSummaries
nested_items.description: Summary information about dataset contents that have been created.

nested_items.name: version
nested_items.description: The version of the dataset contents.

nested_items.name: state
nested_items.description: The state of the dataset contents. Can be one of READY, CREATING, SUCCEEDED, or FAILED.

nested_items.name: reason
nested_items.description: The reason the dataset contents are in this state.

nested_items.name: creationTime
nested_items.description: The actual time the creation of the dataset contents was started.

nested_items.name: scheduleTime
nested_items.description: The time the creation of the dataset contents was scheduled to start.

nested_items.name: completionTime
nested_items.description: The time the dataset content status was updated to SUCCEEDED or FAILED.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: The token to retrieve the next set of results, or null if there are no more results.
